### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Freelance"
}

### Update Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/CATEGORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Freelance Income"
}

### Delete Category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/CATEGORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
